editorialNotes.standard: With best-selling audiobooks, exclusive podcasts, and Audible Originals you won’t find anywhere else, this go-to for audio lovers has one of the biggest spoken-word libraries anywhere. We love how much there is to explore—even beyond books. Stream relaxing sound baths, radio plays and dramatizations, language courses, and more.

There’s only one thing easier than visiting the library: bringing it to you. Meet Libby, an app that lets you log in to your local library to access ebooks, audiobooks, and magazines, all for the reasonable price of free. Sign in, link your library card, and go—it’s that simple.
editorialNotes.short: ‣ For readers, Libby allows you to check out books from your local library—directly on your iPad.
